A Longitudinal Study of Changes in Resting-State Functional Magnetic Resonance 
Imaging Functional Connectivity Networks During Healthy Aging.

Oschmann M(1)(2), Gawryluk JR(2)(3)(4).

Author information:
(1)Faculty of Medicine, University of Cologne, Köln, Germany.
(2)Department of Psychology, University of Victoria, Victoria, British Columbia, 
Canada.
(3)Institute on Aging and Lifelong Health, University of Victoria, British 
Columbia, Canada.
(4)Division of Medical Sciences, University of Victoria, British Columbia, 
